<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, October 11 (Xinhua) -- The Eighth South Asian
Federation (SAF) Games are scheduled to be held here on September
25, 1999, the South Asian Federation Sports Executive Committee
(SAFSEC) decided here Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The regional games will run for 10 days, the committee decided
after a two-day meeting which ended here Sunday.
</P>
<P>
