eighth SAF Games will be completed by March 1999.
</P>
<P>
All the executive members of the SAFSEC pledged to support
Nepal by all means.
</P>
<P>
The games are a biennial event for Bangladesh, Bhutan, India,
the Maldives, Nepal, Pakistan and Sri Lanka, the member countries
of the South Asian Association for Regional Cooperation.
</P>
<P>
The seventh SAF Games were held in December 1995 in Madras,
India. 
