year's Women's soccer World Cup on Sunday as they forced the host
Ukraine to a 1-1 tie in the second game of European playoffs in
Kiev.
</P>
<P>
The draw allowed Germany to advance 6-1 overall in the two-leg
playoff among runners-up in the European group.
</P>
<P>
