firing from close range when the ball slipped out of Ukrainian
goalie Veronika Shulga's hands as she tried to stop a pass from
the left.
</P>
<P>
The host leveled through Svitlana Fryshko in the 50th on a
counterattack.
</P>
<P>
Germany dominated throughout but failed to go ahead on
numerous scoring opportunities. 
