semifinal match to Liaoning at the CFA Cup late September.
</P>
<P>
It had since been rumored that a dozen of corporations
including Beijing-based Gaode Company are setting their eyes on
the lucrative soccer powerhouse,and that the Wanda side are
undergoing negotiations with the corporations, the Shanghai based
paper said.
</P>
<P>
Gaode had sponsored the transfer of two Chinese international
Fan Zhiyi and Sun Jihai to the English Premier League club
Crystal Palace.
</P>
<P>
