transfer since Wanda declared their determination to transfer all
shares."said Huang Ping,the office director of Dalian Wanda
Group.
</P>
<P>
"The reports that we have begun the talks and a dozen of firms
are ready for the takeover are completely unfounded and
baseless."
</P>
<P>
"The players have kept undisturbed in their training and the
remained league matches."added Huang.
</P>
<P>
Gaode Company also spiked the rumor which said that the
company had declared their complete confidence of well managing
the club.
</P>
<P>
"We had no such plan,we are not in the position to take
over the club as far as the financial terms are concerned."
said the senior officials with Gaode company. 
