<HEADLINE> Results of World Junior Badminton Championships </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, October 11 (Xinhua) -- Following are results of the
finals at the World Junior Badminton Championships in
Melbourne,Australia (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Men's singles
