<HEADLINE> Russia Wins World Trampoline Championship </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, October 11 (Xinhua) -- Russia's German Khanytchve
and Irina Karavaeva took the trampoline world championships in
both men's and women's events at Sydney on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
