<HEADLINE> Ferrari Cleansweeps North American Endurance Races </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Ferrari completed a clean
sweep of North American endurance auto races after Wayne Taylor
of the United States won the inaugural Petit Le Mans at Road
Atlanta in Braselton, Georgia on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Ferraris had won the 24 Hours of Daytona and the 12 Hours of
Sebring earlier this year.
</P>
<P>
