<HEADLINE> Two Austrians Killed in Crash </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Bernhard Geramb and his
co-driver Christian Neuhold were killed when their Fiat
Cinquecento crashed in the Steiermark Rally in Austria on
Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The crash occurred on the sixth special stage of the event
which is part of the Austrian national championship.
</P>
<P>
The rally was called off after the tragedy. 
</P>
</TEXT>
